                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I know the handkerchief to be mine, by a little hole in the middle, and the letters "W. H." in the corner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I heard that Mr. Shillibeer wanted an omnibus-man, and went to Greenwich—I wat at the fair, but was never in custody before.</p>
